{"tid":100781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"考左打蚊證書未？","createTime":"2017-01-30T10:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T07:24:39.000Z","uid":4353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d87674403e9a6c1ba580ad03700dc933421ed0","tid":100781,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"住村屋，每日開始入夜5/6點就開始多蚊<br />\n已經唔係打開門，啲蚊為左入屋圍爐取暖，就醒到喺廚房/廁所抽氣扇位sip入嚟<br />\n<br />\n高峰期真係同時出現兩三隻，打完又有打完又有，唔知以為岩岩打嗰啲翻生<br />\n<br />\n有時用蚊拍，一見到佢即拎起開制，就已經唔見咗<br />\n都係用手最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩位都可以搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但當然要記得洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住村屋嘅你，有冇報course學打蚊抑或考咗證書旁身未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684625b25ce30692d063947dd7bb09e715311863","tid":100781,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec94c27cd16fc25f84b776d069e9f0ab4accc6a","tid":100781,"uid":56133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"而家學緊捉蚊 但命中率得三成"},{"pid":"f4d9b0340cc1fdf2137c6a870994637152ae1be3","tid":100781,"uid":76212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"好難考得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139699aac7f07fb5a660f154e950b070318d233e","tid":100781,"uid":7489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我間房高峰期晚晚5.6隻 <br /